{"tid":1859031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會：要求擴大對湖北省入境限制至其他省份","createTime":"2020-02-03T04:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T06:01:03.000Z","uid":125168,"like":43,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"370d4d4c1f91be3a7f3c2132cde7c405af68bfce","tid":1859031,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:51:34.000Z","msg":"工聯會正籌備口罩工廠　料每月產十萬口罩<br />\n7分鐘前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】工聯會屬下的香港醫療人員總工會<span style=\"color: red;\">（17名會員）</span>對有醫護人員罷工表示同情，呼籲他們要堅守崗位。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會則表示，因應本港口罩供應短缺，正籌備設立一個口罩工廠，預計投入服務後每月可生產十萬個口罩，但仍要解決原材料及質量保證等問題。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會亦要求政府更嚴格管制出入境人流，包括按疫情發展，擴大目前針對湖北省居民的入境限制至其他省份。"},{"pid":"3534f0cf14f61432f48e37b8836bd73baae6d1dd","tid":1859031,"uid":125168,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:52:10.000Z","msg":"民賤聯都岀嚟鳩up了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成功爭取"},{"pid":"cc9151d44691b2baf25d833502b225e88ae4affb","tid":1859031,"uid":152476,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:52:52.000Z","msg":"選舉近了"},{"pid":"f7601ae1dd4ffa85f37e66044e804c42d19484f7","tid":1859031,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f1df4acc46d20529e10dc3ace395ee6b6d4cc2","tid":1859031,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cc9151d44691b2baf25d833502b225e88ae4affb","tid":1859031,"uid":152476,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:52:52.000Z","msg":"選舉近了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:53:22.000Z","msg":"八成人撐封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06d1f80b61f4cda2b21962ca48f8cbc9abdc479","tid":1859031,"uid":205482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"工聯會：成功爭取阻止武漢肺炎擴散 多謝中國香港人"},{"pid":"6b8b894daf5a47024a18049ec616abe7686b185e","tid":1859031,